' Benign base package for the PKG-02 security fixture. `generate.py` builds
' this, then rewrites the compiled `.mfp` body into the malicious variant (a
' `run` whose IR does a member access on an Integer) committed under
' tests/syntax/security/pkg-02-type-confusion/packages/. The structured signature
' tables stay valid so the consumer still resolves `run() AS Integer`.
EXPORT FUNC run() AS Integer
  RETURN 42
END FUNC
